title: 112 – på liv och död
overview: 112 – på liv och död is a documentary series where viewers can follow 4 different professional groups. The series includes ambulance staff, hospital staff, firefighters and police during a normal day at work. The cities where the program is recorded are Eksjö, Gävle, Gothenburg, Hässleholm, Kristianstad, Mariehamn, Nyköping, Stockholm, Nässjö, Trollhättan, Vänersborg, Västerås, Uddevalla, Åmål and Östersund.
